Package: narcan
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Working with Multiple Cause of Death Data
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mathew", "Kiang", email = "mathew.kiang@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Monica", "Alexander", email = "monicaalexander@berkeley.edu",
           role = "aut"))
Description: Multiple cause of death (MCOD) data are required for calculating
    opioid deaths, which are defined by both an underlying and a contributory
    cause. This package helps with downloading, importing, munging, and common
    operations on MCOD data, especially in relation to opioid deaths.
URL: https://github.com/mkiang/narcan, https://mkiang.github.io/narcan/
